These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-8-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: gardening, collecting, drawing, rock-climbing, singing, dancing, magic-tricks
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, horse, pony, hedgehog, rabbit, goat
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, folk, gospel, house, metal, rock, salsa
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: lily, zinnia, aconite, bellflower, azalea, iris, tulip
 1. the fan of folk is somewhere to the right of the fan of d&b##5
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the fan of d&b##5
 3. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
 4. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 5. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the person who growsaconite##8
 6. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 7. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 8. the fan of house is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 9. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the person who growslily##8
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person who growslily##7
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the owner of the pony##8
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the person who growsaconite is not to the left of the fan of metal##8
14. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person who growslily##6
15. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
16. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the left of the fan of d&b##8
17. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the person who growsaconite##8
18. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
19. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person who growslily##8
20. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
21. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the fan of rock##1
22. the person who growslily is not to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
23. the person who's hobby is gardening is the fan of metal##1
24. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
25. the person who growsiris is not to the left of the owner of the pony##8
26. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
27. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
28. the fan of salsa is somewhere between the fan of folk and the owner of the horse##7
29. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
30. the person who growsaconite is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
31. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
32. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
33. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who growstulip##8
34. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person who growsiris##6
35. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
36. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
37. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5
38. the fan of metal is not to the left of the owner of the frog##8
39. the owner of the goat is not the person who growsiris##6
40. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5        |       6       |       7       |
| Hobby      | singing   | collecting     | magic-tricks    | gardening      | dancing       | drawing         | rock-climbing |
